data.description: Beautiful all brick/stone home with rear entry garage convenient to parks, shopping, and Village Elementary.  Architectural flare…niches, arches, high ceilings, large and plentiful energy efficient windows, lots of cabinets and granite countertops, gas log fireplace.  Lots of hard tile with color coordinated backsplashes and surrounds.  Wood in the Formal Dining area.  Front and rear patios.  Study with French doors and closet could be a bedroom or another living area.  A huge master, 2 bedrooms and a media/gameroom are upstairs.       Freshly painted and carpeted in 2023.  Gas range, microwave, and dishwasher replaced in 2023. One of two air conditioning condenser/gas furnace systems replaced in 2021. Roof replaced in 2020. Refrigerator replaced in 2018.  Move in ready.
